-- Ron Paul Says He’ll Stay in Race ‘Till the Votes Are Counted’
-- B y   C h r i s   W e l l i s z   a n d   T r i s h   R e g a n
-- 2012-04-30T20:29:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-30/ron-paul-says-he-ll-stay-in-race-till-the-votes-are-counted-.html
Representative  Ron Paul  of Texas
says he will stay in the race for the Republican presidential
nomination until the votes are counted at the party’s
convention. He spoke in an interview on Bloomberg Television’s
“Street Smart.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Wellisz at 
 cwellisz@bloomberg.net  